'''Plothis''' was a resident on [[Tholatin]] during the [[Black Fleet Crisis]] who was an old friend of [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo's]] and [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca's]]. He was [[Death/Legends|killed]] in a squabble with a customer in [[13 ABY/Legends|13 ABY]]. After his death, his employee [[Bracha e'Naso]] would take over Plothis' business.

